<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="dark" lang="pt-BR"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>HORIZON System | Projeto Novos Horizontes</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: "class",
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        "primary": "#001F3F",
                        "deep-blue": "#000B18",
                        "impact-green": "#2ECC71",
                        "impact-green-hover": "#27AE60",
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        "display": ["Plus Jakarta Sans", "sans-serif"]
                    },
                    borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.375rem", "lg": "0.75rem", "xl": "1rem", "full": "9999px"},
                },
            },
        }
    </script>
<style type="text/tailwindcss">
        @layer base {
            body { 
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; 
                @apply bg-deep-blue text-white antialiased;
            }
        }
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }
        .branding-overlay {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 11, 24, 0.8) 0%, rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.4) 100%);
        }
        .input-dark {
            @apply bg-white/5 border-white/10 text-white placeholder:text-slate-500 focus:border-impact-green focus:ring-impact-green/20 transition-all duration-300;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="h-screen overflow-hidden">
<div class="flex h-full w-full">
<section class="hidden lg:flex lg:w-7/12 relative bg-deep-blue overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Futuristic digital map of Africa and students" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover scale-105" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuACzuYzjfoW56RUUwbAZBxbUpyeRM7hiQlJ5eo37Q5emcMg7EFS5Wc287U_HDy4UFGdZyEyF3vnSAVccJlDTChRnu1QpK5jjeJA7xSkig3t0eEJ4egSvNr-wgnlhEahRSH3hwajuHhzeCxWZpFLOBD6-Eswa3MfWHmOpBI9ZVpfIPnGoeKW1-GfQ6CrHMTlsgGzo9MmsNCBV4ZDVRkna5iw6EPqFZSCiB8VxWXUoPrwO223NMTMKcq4XTNt3JgamdNpXGj75h646gI"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 branding-overlay"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-between p-20 w-full">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-impact-green rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(46,204,113,0.3)]">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-3xl font-bold">explore</span>
</div>
<div>
<h1 class="font-extrabold text-3xl leading-none uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white">HORIZON</h1>
<span class="text-[10px] opacity-60 text-white font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">Sistemas Administrativos</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-impact-green/10 border border-impact-green/20 text-impact-green text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
                    Módulo de Gestão Global
                </div>
<h2 class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1] mb-8 tracking-tight">
                    Conectando talentos ao <span class="text-impact-green">futuro digital.</span>
</h2>
<p class="text-xl text-slate-300 font-light max-w-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-impact-green pl-8">
                    A plataforma central para o controle, monitoramento e expansão do Projeto Novos Horizontes em escala global.
                </p>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-white/40 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">security</span>
<span>Criptografia de Ponta</span>
</div>
<div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20"></div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">language</span>
<span>Infraestrutura Distribuída</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-deep-blue to-transparent"></div>
</section>
<section class="w-full lg:w-5/12 bg-[#000d1a] flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-8 sm:px-16 lg:px-24 border-l border-white/5 relative">
<div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(46,204,113,0.03)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="w-full max-w-md relative z-10">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 lg:hidden mb-16">
<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-impact-green rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-2xl font-bold">explore</span>
</div>
<h1 class="font-extrabold text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest text-white">HORIZON</h1>
</div>
<div class="mb-12">
<h3 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-3 tracking-tight">Login do Sistema</h3>
<p class="text-slate-400 font-medium">Insira suas credenciais administrativas para acessar o painel HORIZON.</p>
</div>
<form class="space-y-8">
<div>
<label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" for="email">E-mail Corporativo</label>
<div class="relative group">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-500 text-xl group-focus-within:text-impact-green transition-colors">alternate_email</span>
<input class="w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-4 input-dark rounded-xl text-sm" id="email" name="email" placeholder="nome@horizon.com" required="" type="email"/>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
<label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest" for="password">Senha</label>
<a class="text-xs font-bold text-impact-green hover:text-white transition-colors" href="#">Recuperar acesso</a>
</div>
<div class="relative group">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-500 text-xl group-focus-within:text-impact-green transition-colors">lock</span>
<input class="w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-4 input-dark rounded-xl text-sm" id="password" name="password" placeholder="••••••••••••" required="" type="password"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center">
<input class="h-5 w-5 bg-white/5 border-white/10 text-impact-green rounded focus:ring-impact-green/30 focus:ring-offset-0" id="remember-me" name="remember-me" type="checkbox"/>
<label class="ml-3 block text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium cursor-pointer" for="remember-me">Manter sessão ativa por 30 dias</label>
</div>
<button class="w-full bg-impact-green hover:bg-impact-green-hover text-white font-extrabold py-4.5 rounded-xl shadow-[0_10px_40px_-10px_rgba(46,204,113,0.4)] transition-all transform active:scale-[0.98] flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-lg" type="submit">
<span>Entrar no Sistema</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined font-bold">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</form>
<div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
<p class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
                    Ainda não possui acesso? 
                    <a class="text-white hover:text-impact-green font-bold transition-colors ml-1" href="#">Solicitar Credenciais</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-8 left-0 w-full text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-center">
            © 2024 HORIZON SYSTEM • Projeto Novos Horizontes • Acesso Restrito
        </div>
</section>
</div>

</body></html>
